title: CANAL / MAN ON WATER LOCK barks
description: Barks for the Man on Water Lock.

dialogueTree.title: Man on water lock: ""Barry! Can you hear me, buddy?""
Man on water lock: ""My friend Barry is stuck on the ot..."
dialogueTree.english: "My friend Barry is stuck on the other side."
dialogueTree.polish: „Mój kumpel Barry utknął po drugiej stronie”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Мой сябар Бары завяз на другім баку».

dialogueTree.title: Man on water lock: ""Can't believe no one's coming to f..."
dialogueTree.english: "Can't believe no one's coming to fix this till Wednesday..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Aż się wierzyć nie chce, że nikt tego nie naprawi aż do środy...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Нават не верыцца, што ніхто гэтага не выправіць да серады...»

dialogueTree.title: Man on water lock: ""That butter sign is a write-off fo..."
dialogueTree.english: "That butter sign is a write-off for sure."
dialogueTree.polish: „Ta reklama masła nadaje się już tylko do kasacji”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Гэтая рэклама масла падыходзіць толькі для скасавання».
